      (approx_reachable_list (dloc prog)) cfg'_succ_list) la_en' la_ex'
      (cprog.pid_init_gc (dloc prog)) (visible_prog.pid_interp_gc (\<lambda> x. x \<in> vars_of_ltlc \<phi>)))
      (gci_\<alpha> o run_of_lasso ce)"
